author: Home Repair Tutor
description: ZipDoor installation tips…I seal off rooms when doing dusty drywall work. I love the ZipDoor because it’s easy to install. Also, when it’s not in use, I unzip it and roll the door up. If you’re doing home renovations I highly recommend it.
